WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.320 --> 00:00:05.460
Then Mrs. Sun, how about I get you some fruit?

2
00:00:07.240 --> 00:00:10.420
Mrs. Sun, we have no right to ask what you want to eat.

3
00:00:10.770 --> 00:00:12.110
But this is the Jiang family.

4
00:00:12.470 --> 00:00:16.350
When Mrs. Sun married into the Jiang family, she should abide by the Jiang family's rules.

5
00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:17.540
Look what you said.

6
00:00:18.050 --> 00:00:21.070
It seems that Butler Feng slapped him two days ago

7
00:00:21.070 --> 00:00:22.970
You can't feel the pain at all, right?

8
00:00:23.230 --> 00:00:26.030
Just now when we were cooking in the kitchen

9
00:00:26.030 --> 00:00:27.650
Found a silver spoon missing.

10
00:00:28.230 --> 00:00:30.390
I wonder if Mrs. Sun saw it.

11
00:00:31.160 --> 00:00:32.420
Hey, it’s really gone.

12
00:00:32.619 --> 00:00:34.080
You don't mean to accuse me wrongly.

13
00:00:34.480 --> 00:00:35.440
That would be strange.

14
00:00:35.440 --> 00:00:37.850
Except for the three of us in the kitchen

15
00:00:37.850 --> 00:00:39.110
Only you have been here

16
00:00:39.450 --> 00:00:40.770
That thing is gone

17
00:00:40.770 --> 00:00:42.650
There has to be an explanation

18
00:00:43.060 --> 00:00:45.040
What tricks do you want to play again?

19
00:00:45.040 --> 00:00:45.940
To show innocence

20
00:00:45.940 --> 00:00:47.840
We'd better do a body search.

21
00:00:47.930 --> 00:00:50.210
Someone's hands and feet are unclean

22
00:00:50.620 --> 00:00:52.140
I don’t have it anymore

23
00:00:52.360 --> 00:00:53.400
What about you?

24
00:00:53.580 --> 00:00:54.240
Neither do we

25
00:00:54.240 --> 00:00:55.160
Neither do we

26
00:00:55.160 --> 00:00:58.390
What should I do?

27
00:00:58.390 --> 00:01:00.750
Who thinks you are such a loser?

28
00:01:00.750 --> 00:01:03.100
Mrs. Young

29
00:01:03.100 --> 00:01:05.319
We are also doing it for your innocence.

30
00:01:05.319 --> 00:01:06.180
It doesn't matter

31
00:01:06.180 --> 00:01:08.610
My innocence is not as important as eating

32
00:01:08.610 --> 00:01:09.860
If you don't translate it

33
00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:14.200
Don't blame us for taking action.

34
00:01:16.400 --> 00:01:19.660
I didn’t expect our young lady Sun to be a thief.

